    "description": "Q+ Technology – A New Generation of Flare! \nQUIET! Perfect for stage and studio!\nBRIGHT! Over 1000 Watt brightness (in Turbo Mode)\nPOWERFUL OPTIONS! Three modes for improved performance + full compatibility with earlier generation Flares. Perfect for retrofitting in existing systems.\n• Theatre Mode: Quiet, effectively silent operation, 8% brighter;\n• Turbo Mode: 40% brighter, yet still very quiet!\n• The same world class dimming, colours, smoothness, control features, and flicker-free performance;\n• Calibration mode allows matching of intensity AND COLOUR of Flares of all vintages and types.",
